title: NOAA, 5 day precipitation forecast, USA, 02/08/2010
name: NOAA, 5 day precipitation forecast, USA, 02/08/2010
description: This dataset comes from the NOAA, The National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) is a federal agency focused on the condition of the oceans and the atmosphere. this dataset shows the forecast for precipitation in the United States for the 5 days following september 12th, 2008. this includes rainfall from Hurricane Ike
